messages.content: Please send all relevant info, thank you!
Is it just my rate you want or for packages?
Please feel free to mail your rate card to Tavish (tavish@elppin.com).

Hello

I just wanted to reach out to see if you have any up and coming projects for my services of art direction and styling? 

I am fully licensed with a kitas so able to organize shoots in Bali. 

Im now offering some amazing packages working with different teams and a variety of budgets to cater to everyone. 

We can create anything from:

Campaigns

Lookbooks

Ways to wear and style reels to increase sales on items that are not selling.

Personal branding - designer portraits

Brand stories, inspiration behinds and so much more. 

I have recently updated my website so you can have a look at examples of all of this. 

Please feel free to reach out if you have any up and coming projects you would like to involve me in. 

Thank you 

Www.maycortazzi.com
